verbose_text: Furthermore, although the plasma insulin levels of the ADMSCs group were significantly higher than those in the control group (9.22 +/-1.89 vs. 6.73 +/-1.24, respectively; P = 0.003) (XREF_FIG), they were highest in the ADMSCs-BET group than in the control or ADMSCs groups (13.64 +/-1.12 vs. 6.73 +/-1.24 and 9.22 +/-1.89, respectively; P < 0.001).
